data.description: Beautiful Home with Vintage Charm and Modern Upgrades!Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this residence combines timeless charm with modern comforts. Step inside and experience the warmth and coziness of this unique property. Classic Formica countertops, well-maintained and in original condition, adding a touch of nostalgia to the heart of the home. Elegant white cabinets, original and meticulously preserved, providing ample storage space for all your kitchen essentials. The kitchen flooring was tastefully upgraded in 2018-2019, ensuring durability and style for your culinary adventures. 12 minutes from Busco Beach and ATV Park, less then 20 from Herman Park and 20 from Wayne Community College!
